N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 600.13 - Adjustments in schedule for compliance review or complaint processing

State Regulations

If, in the judgment of the State Division of Human Rights, a particular situation warrants and requires special processing and either
expedited or extended determination, it shall take the steps necessary to
permit such determination if it finds that no person or party affected by such
determination will be prejudiced by such special processing. Notes
